To further investigate the existence of the dipolar glass phase, the frequency dependences of ε* were approximated by the superposition of two Cole–Cole processes that describes both cation relaxation and conductivity effects59:1ε*ω=ε∞+∑jΔεj1+(iωτj)1−αj.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
